title: The Reason Lunchbox Wants To Go On Strike + Luke Combs Stops By For The Friday Morning Conversation
itunes:title: The Reason Lunchbox Wants To Go On Strike + Luke Combs Stops By For The Friday Morning Conversation
description:
Lunchbox threatens to go on strike next week. Luke Combs stops by for the Friday Morning Conversation to celebrate the release of his Deluxe Album "This One's For You Too." Bobby serves up some Judge Common Sense to a caller. Also, Amy's lost credit card finds its way back to her.
